
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        .container { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: auto; border: 1px solid #ddd; }
        .header { padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-bottom: 2px solid #eee; background-color: #f8f8f8; }
        .content { padding: 30px 20px; line-height: 1.6; }
        .otp { 
            font-size: 36px; 
            font-weight: bold; 
            letter-spacing: 5px; 
            margin: 20px 0; 
            color: #ffffff;
            background-color: #007bff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-align: center;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .footer { padding: 15px; font-size: 12px; color: #777; background-color: #f4f4f4; text-align: center; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="{{logoUrl}}" alt="DevGo Logo" style="width: 150px; height: auto;" />
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello {{fullName}},</p>

            <p>Welcome to DevGo Courier Service!</p>

            <p>To complete your registration, please use the following One-Time Password (OTP):</p>
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <div class="otp">{{otp}}</div>
            </div>
            
            <p>This code is valid for the next 1 minutes.</p> 

            <p>Please enter this OTP in the app to verify your email address.</p>

            <p>Thank you for choosing us!<br>
            <strong>The DevGo Courier Service Team</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2025 DevGo. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>